Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:03.10,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Raimon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:05.27,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the bike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:09.07,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just ride a motorcycle \Nto school without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:09.98,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Aight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:12.40,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a hooligan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.79,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Takaragi, you should have stopped her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:15.74,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.77,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who told me not to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:21.75,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,And I live real far from school, \Nso it's a royal pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.01,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's hooligan talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:24.00,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:31.00,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad... you came to school...
