Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.86,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Raimon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:23.08,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since middle school, \NI've always admired her confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:27.33,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,We challenged her to a bottle rocket contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:33.47,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I may have lost that match, but I finally\N told her what was on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:39.09,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see Raimon-san \Nback at school again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.16,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi-san, bona-morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.04,DefaultTop,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good... mati...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.04,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, bona-morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.11,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Mativuu, Nasshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:06.80,Default,Yao,0000,0000,0000,,She has been learning the violin \Nsince she was five years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:11.06,Default,Yao,0000,0000,0000,,and she is aiming for music \Ncollege in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:11.96,Default,English Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.31,Default,English Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Next, roster number fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.13,Default,English Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Number fourteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.13,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:23.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.33,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}x{\i0} squared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.89,Default,English Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,This is English class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.64,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.38,Default,English Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Don't doze off in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:37.40,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki, come eat lunch with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.49,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone, bun-haired nutjob.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.63,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try asking her again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.78,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.85,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to rush your meal.
