Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:05.05,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,1)\fs12\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1402A0&\4c&HC3FBFF&\pos(321,231.5)}Nice and Hot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:02.05,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I survived another whole day of school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.05,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats some creamy potato soup \Nfor wrapping up the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.18,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Matataki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.16,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Let's share a can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.56,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't ever dial it down, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to take a nice, big gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.80,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.51,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yu seems happier than usual today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:20.32,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's because you're here, \NMatataki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.58,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.20,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand all this yapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is someone embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:28.99,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That stubborn attitude is just \Nhiding your embarrassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.21,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'll tear off those buns of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.46,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki-chan looks like \Nshe's having fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.51,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,R-Raimon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:43.97,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anything today \Nth-that gave you trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:47.95,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-If there's anything you need, \Njust let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:50.72,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do what I-I can to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.84,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.04,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You should worry about yourself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.94,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.11,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:05.81,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:09.33,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,When she was launching rockets with \NHaruno and the bun-haired nutjob,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.50,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she showed some guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:15.56,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment she's thrown into \Na school setting, she turns into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:21.55,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess I'm not one to talk, \Nconsidering I wasn't attending at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Matataki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:27.32,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna try launching a cool \Nrocket like the one back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.18,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the same wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.39,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you could lend her \Nsome of that backbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.80,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.08,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,It can serve as your next step up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.25,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd love to make one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.90,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:45.78,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,The parts don't come cheap, though, \Nso the one problem is the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.33,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,How much can you spare in club funds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:54.81,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're not, um, in a club or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.00,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's all out-of-pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.50,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Just call us free dreamers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.54,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:02.63,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Without any means of funding, you won't \Neven be able to make rockets for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.20,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.45,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Itemized expenses necessary \Nfor a bona-fide rocket launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.17,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I summed it all up, so read it over!
