Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.89,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:18.96,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.90,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a club?! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.21,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.34,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.53,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We're very sorry to interrupt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.28,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We were hoping to start up a new club,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.53,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,so could we please have an application form?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.04,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, an application form?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.66,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,There ya go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.71,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.97,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You could learn something from Haruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:43.67,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last one I want to hear that from!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.92,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Summary of club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.87,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,"Rocket assembly" should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.99,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,What should we name the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.81,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,A flash of inspiration!
