Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.40,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The Dream*Rocket Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.21,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.51,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's a one-of-a-kind name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.49,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote this in pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.27,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't erase it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.07,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.81,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.29,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.30,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.33,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord4\fnComic Sans MS\c&HA87C76&\3c&HE0C7BB&}Teachers' Office
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.33,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord1\fnComic Sans MS\c&HA87C76&\3c&H70554C&}Teachers' Office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:24.77,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, am I thinking of the right rockets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.34,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The kind that fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.82,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The kind that fly into outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.34,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,O-Outer space?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:37.12,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Our school {\i1}is{\i0} pretty lenient when it comes \Nto extracurricular activities, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:40.10,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me an idea with a \Nbetter chance of getting accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.35,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,You can just say it's a volunteer club, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.66,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:46.66,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Be a little pickier than that! Pickier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.44,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.50,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:54.62,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're... s-serious about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.62,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(354,1)\fs30\fnArial Black\c&HB8A5F7&\shad1.5\bord1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(320,146.5)}Blah           {\c&HF88487&}blah\N{\c&H51B0EF&}yadda           {\c&HF565AC&}yadda
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.03,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Umika and I are trying\Nto go out into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:59.00,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Now, the school already\Nhas an astronomy club,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:59.00,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Assembling models\Nof solid-propellant rockets
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:08:00.01,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}I've a-always been interested \Nin rockets and outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.01,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}You need a rocket\Nfor that, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.01,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}will be the key focus of our \Nactivities for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:02.01,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}but their primary goal \Nis to observe the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:04.99,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}A-And we all tried\Nmaking bottle rockets...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:04.01,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}While they may be replicas, \Nwe are building real rockets,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:07.88,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}So we need to make one,\Nand Matataki said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.21,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}In contrast, our goal is\Nto research and develop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:07.88,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}so parts like the frame and\Nengine cost a significant amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:07.88,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}N-Now, we want to make\Nsomething more advanced...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.88,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}methods for going\Nto outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:09.88,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.63,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you've been up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.64,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.88,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's because we were working in secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:17.74,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.58,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The secret's out of the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.97,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make an exception \Nfor you, Emihara-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.55,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.19,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.78,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see what I can do to get it greenlit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.45,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.49,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You betcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:39.86,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,So come up with a more \Nconcrete idea by next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:41.12,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.04,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Also!
