Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.68,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Think of a snazzier name for the club, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.61,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:48.86,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I was so proud of that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.17,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,No surprise there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.07,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.07,DefaultTop,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you... very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.20,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can secure some club funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.43,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can make a big ol' rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.09,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:03.87,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,How large should it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:07.82,FlashbackItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I want to find \Na place where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:12.30,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:19.70,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you looking for a place to belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.30,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Now you have one, so good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.53,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.71,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.46,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.50,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,That club form just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:38.47,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I took the liberty of filling out \Nwho'd be in charge, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.78,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,So good luck with your new position, prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:46.97,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.95,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to be our club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.36,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.83,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I wanna be vice president!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.99,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Overruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.63,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.43,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.09,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Why her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.50,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, what a surprise, though.
