Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:10.18,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I took her to be one of \Nmy more reserved students,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.80,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,but Konohoshi as president?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:15.51,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,And Raimon's in the club, at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:20.76,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this form is proof that a \Ntiny spark can set off big changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.51,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make sure this goes through, \Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:30.40,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, l-looks like it'll be a little \Nlonger before we can begin our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.04,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.77,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to first discuss \Nwhat our club will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.60,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Just come up with something \Nthat sounds good during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.88,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,During class...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.92,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you working on something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.78,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I bet I didn't miss anything interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.46,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.09,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki's a hooligan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:46.94,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Cram it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:49.33,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you sleeping the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.56,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, tomorrow's another day of \Nshowing up to school whenever,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.74,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,and doing whatever I like at my desk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.84,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe school's easier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.60,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you giving me that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.27,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you forgot, Matataki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.55,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,A-About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.69,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you the notice, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:17.73,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H22&\fad(697,763)\fnComic Sans MS\fs40\bord1\pos(320,90)}A few weeks ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.30,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a handout from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.95,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important, \Nso make sure you look it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.02,DefaultItalics,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use it as scratch paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:28.78,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, the first-years are going \Non a two-day study camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:29.75,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.54,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:31.99,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.40,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.16,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,This is news to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.64,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it a trip to remember!
