Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:52.14,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, it feels as though \NI'm surrounded by sparkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:03.98,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Launching a bottle rocket \Nfor the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.36,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Going shopping with my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.93,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming friends with Raimon-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.95,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,These sparkles...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.88,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What lies behind the sparkling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:22.64,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.83,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,spinning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.91,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.60,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.88,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.88,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan's feeling short of breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:33.94,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:36.97,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We're still at the base of the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.69,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Good work making the climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.86,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.70,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I know we just made it to the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.70,DefaultTop,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:49.42,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,but it's time for our workshop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.87,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.88,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you've looked over the reading \Nmaterials I gave out in advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.62,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Get into your groups!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.71,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Not a lot of happy campers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:04.09,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(487,558)\fs30\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H272C29&\3c&HF9FFFF&\frz10.57\pos(151.5,28)}Weary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.86,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Choosing this high school was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:07.55,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's the most dramatic \Nreaction I've ever gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.39,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Matataki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.70,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same group!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.59,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see you two later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.12,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.02,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.39,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll enjoy some of the reading!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.48,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.94,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What do we need to do for this workshop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.28,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
