Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:28.80,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Using the given documents \Nand literary works
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:32.95,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,written about th-this mountain's \Nsurrounding environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.45,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,e-each group will d-decide on \Na topic and create a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.55,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Docu...ments?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.76,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}did{\i0} get them in advance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.76,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord4\fnComic Sans MS\c&HA87C76&\3c&HF7F2E5&}Conference Room 1
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.76,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord1\fnComic Sans MS\c&HA87C76&\3c&H70554C&}Conference Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.11,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.01,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the workshop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:53.77,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kagami, group leader and class president,\Nand I'll be in charge of the proceedings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.60,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all work hard together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:02.94,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's take turns and share the reading\Nthat you thought was most interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:09.84,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I thought... the essay on \Npage 21 was interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.16,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.16,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.86,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,How do you read this kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.88,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.74,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.04,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:24.67,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If only Takaragi-san and \NRaimon-san were in our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:28.55,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next, can you tell us what \Nyou thought, Konohoshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:34.01,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,M-My mind's gone completely blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.93,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:52.93,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought the essay on \Npage 21 was i-interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:54.45,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(238,1)\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\fs10\c&H66666D&\3c&HFEFFFD&\frz12.29\move(14.37,306,76.75,306,29,3825)}Study Camp\NWorkshop Reading\NLiterature
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.45,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:15:01.65,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,th-this author's novels a-always \Ntake place in w-winter,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:06.11,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,b-but this essay alone uses \Nspring as its theme...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.25,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,This is... sort of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:52.80,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I always hated being in situations like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.37,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,but not this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:16:00.19,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's sparkling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:06.02,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I met Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.90,Flashback,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:16.35,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If all goes well with the club, \NI can do more for Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.16,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.91,Flashback,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,So good luck with your new position, prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:25.81,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She must have been kidding about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.20,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I can't be club president!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:32.05,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but worry just \Nas I'm about to go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:37.83,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, Akeuchi-san still \Nhasn't come back from the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.31,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:43.63,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Did she end up being abducted \Nby a fellow alien?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:46.69,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:49.09,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.16,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.09,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.26,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.71,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.47,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:06.73,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:11.73,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was worried because \Nyou didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:12.83,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.27,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a worrywart, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:17.93,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I ended up being abducted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:20.87,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:21.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.72,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's sparkling like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.89,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots more stars than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.58,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I found myself lost in thought out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:36.46,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,wondering whether one of these \Ncould be my home planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.51,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:43.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:45.77,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Forget what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.98,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, it's not like \NI feel lonely or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.40,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You know that I love life here on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.15,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-We'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.90,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make it into space! I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:19:02.02,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san has always been there \Nto guide my dreams and my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.30,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why it's my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.41,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:13.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Back when we first met, I think... \Nmy dream wasn't a very realistic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.17,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that's not true anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:19.67,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takaragi-san and Raimon-san \Nare here to help us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:22.54,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-And our new club, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.16,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,So I promise I'll take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:30.61,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll be the one to make \Nall your wishes come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.94,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:37.11,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't put it into words very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:41.46,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is, I have lots more to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.90,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, Umika...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.11,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:52.45,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,All of them, to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:56.96,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.43,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.77,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.44,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why am {\i1}I{\i0} the one apologizing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.04,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you two
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:17.43,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's foreheadpathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.59,Default,Matataki,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.28,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you two doing here?
