Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.76,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:09.75,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My tiny dream is moving forward, \Nlittle by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:15.02,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I know that this dream isn't \Njust a fairy tale now!
